      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable and well-maintained 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i finished in classic Alpine White. This vehicle strikes a perfect balance for someone seeking luxury performance without the new-car price tag. The exterior remains sharp and glossy, though close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the hood and small scuffs on the rear bumper consistent with standard use. The 19-inch alloy wheels show some light curb rash but remain structurally perfect. Inside, the cabin is a highlight: the Black Dakota leather upholstery is supple, free of any rips or significant wear, and the interior has never been smoked in. All electronic amenities\u2014including the panoramic glass sunroof, dual-zone climate control, and the iDrive navigation system\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in great shape; it has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and a fresh set of air filters installed. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts effortlessly. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the brake pads were replaced last season. It\u2019s a solid, honest vehicle that is ready for its next owner. Clean title and service records available.",
